			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.requiemoftheoutcast.com/podcast9eps/butcherprerelease.pdf"><img src="http://www.requiemoftheoutcast.com/podcast9eps/99jpg.jpg" alt="Ecru" /></a></p>

<p>Here&#8217;s a special prerelease of a new podcasting first: a full comic book distributed exclusively via podcast!</p>

